com.facebook.rendercore

Class MountDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.rendercore.MountDelegate

  • public class MountDelegate
extends java.lang.Object
    Can be passed to a MountState to override default mounting behaviour and control which items get mounted or unmounted.
